
```python
from ai_readiness import AssessmentFramework

# Initialize assessment
assessment = AssessmentFramework()

# Configure for your organization
config = {
    'company_size': 'enterprise',
    'industry': 'financial_services',
    'compliance_requirements': ['SOX', 'PCI-DSS'],
    'use_cases': ['fraud_detection', 'risk_modeling']
}

# Run comprehensive assessment
results = assessment.run_full_assessment(config)

# Generate executive report
assessment.generate_executive_report(results, output_path='./reports/')

# Calculate ROI projections
roi_analysis = assessment.calculate_roi(results, investment_range=(500000, 2000000))
print(f"Projected ROI: {roi_analysis['roi_percentage']:.1f}%")
```
